            "text": "The thrailorn attacks a single foe in a wild, pain-fueled flurry. The thrailorn makes one jaws Strike and two thorn Strikes in any order. These attacks must target the same creature. These attacks count toward the thrailorn's multiple attack penalty, but the multiple attack penalty doesn't increase until after the thrailorn makes all their attacks.",
